Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(avant)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine Impacter…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:02:00.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:02:00.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うためだった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}漱漱而下的淚水 在風中飄散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こぼれ行く涙風が連れて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:27.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以生疏的動作 無數次伸出手去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:27.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}慣れない仕草でその先へ何度も手を伸ばした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:33.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個不善於表達而受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:33.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}言葉足らずで傷つけた人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:38.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}現在已經背負起不可磨滅的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:38.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう取り消せない過去を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:42.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏出了新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:42.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏み出して行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:48.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:48.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:55.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うための理由だった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:55.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:03:01.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日があるたったそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:03:01.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只因為這一個理由 就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:07.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕ら生きる意味になって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:07.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那將成為我們生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:14.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そしてまた日が照らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:14.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}太陽將再次照耀大地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KILL-T-TANG突破第一防禦圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Earthengine接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了新的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Driver能聽到我說話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔 叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諮詢系統還沒有啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(540,660)}consultation system
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法輔助Earthengine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了 大地？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是彼得·韋斯特威利智
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號蝴蝶 你能聽到我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(465,660)}Code Papillon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是代號蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況我已經把握了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我希望你能當Earthengine的飛行指導員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(945,660)}Flight Direction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借你們的線路一用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Driver 你能聽到我說話吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當我是你的同伴魔法少女就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在正身處戰場 這你能懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂不懂我是不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道如果讓眼前這傢伙到達地球就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部Earthengine現在充滿了Livlaster的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能驅動它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…那你是如何乘上去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道被槍給操縱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須將那傢伙打倒是我自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍只是借給了我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個普通的高中生而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 操作由我來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你負責提供動力就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握緊Livlaster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就一動不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不直接操作是很難控制的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果害死你 就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…會死？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果爸爸不幸死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候肯定是笑著離去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想…死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打中它就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生命力能量嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你等一下…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是讓你這樣打！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺有趣的 我喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊KILL-T-TANG成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好糟糕的一場戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號蝴蝶 感謝你的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其打敗的是那位Earth Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦 Globe先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我私自作出的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考慮到形勢的緊迫性 所以希望你能原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種情況下 能輔助Earthengine的飛行指導員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我所認識的人當中只有她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是近期我想挖到這基地來的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會將她的資料給你過目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和9年前相比 形態明顯不一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而推測我們所擔心的KILL-T-TANG的活動期已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在整個衛星基地已經將備戰狀態的等級提升到1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(735,660)}DEFCON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦圈內的所有衝擊兵器進入了臨戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒收到Earth Driver已經配屬給種子島的報告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine啟動順槳系統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(800,660)}feathering system
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自動返航模式進入種子島歸還軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(430,660)}Autocruise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Salty Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空港周邊的封鎖已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是種子島總部 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會是Earth Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(144,74)}槍{\c&HBB6E1A&}名{\r}叫Livlaster
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現任何身體異常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少目前沒發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二把Livlaster似乎已經出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這種可能性 你完全沒跟我們說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有跟我提及過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們再慢慢來討論這問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經退燒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟你談談——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道估計是你產生的圓虹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這Globe表面上是以促進和平為目的的國際性宇宙開發基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實上 它是一個和那些異星文明侵略者戰鬥的防衛組織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 這些都是機密事項
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 爸爸的死…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把槍你是從哪裡得到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當注意到的時候已經拿在手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩具沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰允許你們使用引導裝置了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(740,660)}lead gears
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的處置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她這樣誠實又老實的人當然無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有突然間使用自己奇異能力的人在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哲平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的女孩子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是花覺醒時在場的那位少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導裝置應該是禁止使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們Salty Dog不僅僅是Globe的視察官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西我現在玩得更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也是內務調查官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這是越權行為！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我有權利在緊急時刻排除風險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我來實現那時的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平也來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把這隻動物放出籠子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會確保不會再讓那樣的人碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不是他自己開的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是槍讓他開的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得Livlaster這個能量產生裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是槍 而是槍形態的異次元生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 牠有自我意識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牠的意識驅動了Earthengine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想比較妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:14:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說Livlaster為了驅動Earthengine而利用了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 調查結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他發誓保證保密後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就送他回本土吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然KILL-T-TANG已經進入了活動期…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前狀況能允許這樣做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於Machine Goodfellow的實戰實驗的日程還沒有確定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三技術開發部提出了不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這事不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓Designer Child隨意制定開發日程？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的方針
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們過於自由的話不危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主模塊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(600,660)}Ego Block
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…毫髮無損
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們在自主模塊狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以使用混沌連接來進行超空間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(580,660)}Entangle Link
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們過於接近地球圈時自主模塊實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會發生力比多爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(725,660)}libido burst
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一段路就不得不依靠KILL-T-TANG進行通常空間的移動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們是掌握了我們的特性而佈置防禦系統的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能小看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法稱心如意才叫人生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 擊毀了Malkin的衝擊兵器是怎樣的一個傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是使用Livlaster的載人衝擊兵器！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告訴我 讓他們自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對Machine Goodfellow開發來說最有效率的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告訴你？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 久部社長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天海道那邊好像有所行動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這就知道了啊 佩服佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種說話方式還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣更有電腦風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的秘書小仁美今天也穿了一套很騷的正裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不邀請她約會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KILL-T-TANG到達地球的時刻不會比預測的時間早吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的模擬預測是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間Globe應該會爭取到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:17:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今晚 你一定能上了小仁美的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家已經完全做好準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選中的人類會生存下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是被我選中的人類才會活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止Macbeth革命的成功率是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕克不會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做法我不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是個孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是又再像昨天那樣搗亂 我就很難辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學部長 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是昨天那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這基地的科學部長 彼得·韋斯特威利智
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要查問關於Livlaster的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也讓他們二人參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上有很多事情不需要你去知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這真叫人興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所得到的槍是第二把
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為那Livlaster槍是一種兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是身為持有者的這個女孩——羅塔花卻沒辦法使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們訓練了他——嵐哲平作為候補
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅塔花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你叫花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學部長 你說得太多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間也需要他來協助這個計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 昨天你想帶他們出去做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看我的飛鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛鏢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓她看看飛鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說飛鏢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 和她約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個笨蛋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼昨天他們兩人突然痛苦起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人是保護觀察對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為一個必要的安全預防措施 我給他們佩戴了引導裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想從基地的隔離區裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的傳感塔就會檢測到 並給予他們輕微的頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們做了什麼錯事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非如此 但他們很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們擁有特殊的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 從今天開始你也會成為他們當中的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向總部提出申請
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼能使用Livlaster 之後我們會慢慢調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初射後還能保住性命 你就心懷感激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(360,660)}initial shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我並不是這樣覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我的Livlaster在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像誤會了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本身 所謂「你」的Livlaster根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查問就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在海岸邊等你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏大地是真夏太陽的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine也是他父親給起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長的血統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他乘上了Earthengine也是命運的安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我口中說出命運這個詞 不太相襯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏大地的引導裝置 進入了警戒模式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著這東西真辛苦呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保管庫中的Livlaster產生了強烈的生命力反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 皮茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算出去嗎 花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想看飛鏢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛鏢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 大地為什麼會回到這島來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來兌現承諾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我想起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島上吹的風很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ふわり風は彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}清風徐徐吹向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}涙も連れて行ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}請把我的眼淚也一起帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}星ほどの思い出たちだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使是那些堪比繁星的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いいことばっかじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也不全是快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}瞬いて　君と出逢えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個閃爍的瞬間 我與你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ねぇ　こんなに近くで遠い今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今天 這個近在咫尺又如此遙遠的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}始まる合図はぽつりわたしを呼ぶ声聞こえてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我聽到了那個開始的信號 在輕輕地呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}愛してるよりもっと形のない言葉探して行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要尋找比「我愛你」更加飄渺的情話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すぐ側に歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我從你身邊走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:50.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さよならよりもそっと涙が紡いだ恋は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:50.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}比「再見」更會在不經意間催人淚下的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日も右ポケットに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明天依然緊攥在右邊口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界は声に溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界充滿著美妙的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やっと見つけたんだ　君のとなりを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我終於找到了與你並肩的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西久保叔叔…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是司令家 我以及哲平還有花和燈里將一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.25,0:24:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是KILL-T-TANG又再次襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Salty Dog使了陰謀詭計
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.08,0:24:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我駕駛著出故障的Earthengine出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.98,0:24:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 Earthengine 第3話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.49,0:24:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albion的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.02,0:24:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine expand！

